âœ… As you move from On-Premises â†’ IaaS â†’ PaaS â†’ SaaS,
your responsibility decreases and the providerâ€™s responsibility increases.

ğŸ’¡ Real-World Example Summary
Scenario	Type	Your Responsibility	Providerâ€™s Responsibility
You host your own server in your office	On-premises	Everything (hardware, OS, patches, data)	None
